Source: ooze
Package: ooze
Version: @VERSION@
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Ooze Desktop <ooze@localhost>
Homepage: https://github.com/Zadagast/ooze
Depends: mutter, libmutter-18-0, xwayland, dbus-user-session, libgtk-4-1, libadwaita-1-0, libvte-2.91-gtk4-0, libgtop-2.0-11, libudisks2-0, libpipewire-0.3-0t64, libgdk-pixbuf-2.0-0, libcairo2, libpango-1.0-0, libpangocairo-1.0-0, libx11-6, libglib2.0-0t64
Recommends: appmenu-gtk3-module, appmenu-gtk-module-common, appmenu-registrar
Suggests: xsettingsd
Description: Ooze Wayland desktop (Mutter 18)
 Ooze is a Mutter-based desktop shell with Spot, Command, King, and related
 apps. Installs a GDM Wayland session (Ooze) plus a nested ooze-session
 launcher for testing inside an existing login.
 .
 Requires host Mutter 18 (Ubuntu 26.04). Xwayland stays enabled so classic
 GTK3 apps can feed the global menu via appmenu-gtk-module.
